thread.title: HOLLY
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by HOLLY

author: HOLLY
title: HOLLY
text:
Rented a Kia automatic hatch back. Car in good condition, rates were reasonable, and check-in and check-out was friendly and hassle free. What more do you need?
Only criticism is excess for damages is a bit outrageous at $4000 so would suggest people take out insurance to remove this.
